@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .section img {
                border-radius: 10px;
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
            }

                .section img:hover {
                    transform: scale(1.05);
                }

            .section p {
                margin-top: 20px;
                color: #666;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p>This Privacy Policy describes how KhumaloCraft Emporium ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and shares personal information of users of this website (the "Site").</p>

        <h1>Information We Collect</h1>
        <p>We may collect personal information from users in a variety of ways, including, but not limited to, when users visit our site, register on the site, place an order, subscribe to the newsletter, respond to a survey, fill out a form, and in connection with other activities, services, features, or resources we make available on our Site.</p>

        <h1>How We Use Collected Information</h1>
        <p>We may use personal information collected from users for various purposes, including, but not limited to, improving customer service, processing transactions, sending periodic emails, and administering contests, promotions, surveys, or other site features.</p>

        <h1>Sharing Your Personal Information</h1>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent users' personal information to others. We may share generic aggregated demographic information not linked to any personal information regarding visitors and users with our business partners, trusted affiliates, and advertisers for the purposes outlined above.</p>

        <h1>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.</p>
         
        <br></br><br></br><br></br>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
